hcc_text: Vandervoort Avenue is in the middle third in Brooklyn for pedestrian deaths and serious injuries per mile.
info: At Vandervoort Avenue at Meeker Avenue, Bqe Westbound Exit 34 and Apollo Street, there were 7 injuries in crashes between 2008 and 2012.
